###1.编译spark
```shell
./make-distribution.sh --tgz
```

###2.上传到hdfs
###3.配置spark-env.sh配置文件,
* 增加SPARK_EXECUTOR_URI
```shell
export SPARK_EXECUTOR_URI=hdfs:///spark-1.4.1-bin-2.2.0.tgz
```
* 增加MESOS_NATIVE_JAVA_LIBRARY


###4.添加mesos salve 参数
```shell
./mesos-slave.sh ... --hadoop_home=/opt/hadoop-2.7.1 
如果不添加hadoop_home他就不知道hadoop -fs 命令位置
```